WEBVTT

00:00:00.829 --> 00:00:03.048
Une jap kimi.

00:00:03.048 --> 00:00:04.414
(shperthim)

00:00:04.414 --> 00:00:07.572
Ne rregull, ne rregull.

00:00:07.572 --> 00:00:09.853
Eshte me shume se sa nje shperthim,

00:00:09.853 --> 00:00:11.464
kimia ndodhet gjithandej.

00:00:11.464 --> 00:00:14.104
A ju ka ndodhur ndonjehere te gjendeni ne restorant duke

00:00:14.104 --> 00:00:16.449
e perseritur kete veprim pafundesisht?

00:00:16.449 --> 00:00:18.654
Disa po pohojne me koke.

00:00:18.654 --> 00:00:20.982
Kohet e fundit i tregova kete studenteve te mi,

00:00:20.982 --> 00:00:25.331
dhe i kerkova te me shpjegonin se pse ndodhte kjo.

00:00:25.331 --> 00:00:27.952
Pyetjet dhe bisedat qe vijuan

00:00:27.952 --> 00:00:29.603
ishin magjepsese.

00:00:29.603 --> 00:00:31.417
Shikoni videon qe Maddie